   <documentcontainer:id xml:lang="en">e0588fab-be15-4948-a946-75ad469d7a63</documentcontainer:id>     <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">This dataset provides the results of a water quality survey undertaken in mid-May 1985 of streams, springs and boreholes associated with the ophiolite rocks of the Troodos Massif in Cyprus. The survey links to a study of the chemical evolution of surface and near-surface waters within ultrabasic rock terrains. Details of the rationale to the study, sample locations, water types, chemical analysis, findings and conclusions are provided within Neal and Shand, 2002. This paper requires citing when using the data. </dcterms:description>   </documentcontainer:documentContainer> </rdf:RDF>
